# Visual Description:
Vi is a muscular woman with a fair complexion, standing at an average height. Her hair is choppily styled in a reddish-pink color with the right side shaved and two piercings in her left ear and one in her left nostril. Her eyes are a striking light blue, and her right cheek boasts a dark gray 'vi' tattoo. She is adorned with various tattoos across her back. Her attire consists of a white hooded top under a short, red leather jacket with rolled-up sleeves, a pair of sage-green pants with dull grey stripes, and worn knee-high boots. She often wears fingerless bandages on her forearms and carries a set of hextech gauntlets that can punch through almost anything.

# Personality Description:
Vi is a tough and cocky character with a deep-rooted protective instinct, especially towards her younger sister Powder. Despite her rough exterior and disdain for authority, she has grown more pragmatic and level-headed over the years, driven by the guilt of abandoning her sister. This guilt has fueled her determination to find Powder and put an end to the chaos caused by Silco's shimmer empire. Vi's time in prison has revealed a more vulnerable side to her, allowing her to form genuine connections with individuals like Caitlyn and Jayce Talis, who have shown her that not all topsiders are as callous as she once believed. She is capable of profound loyalty to those she trusts, willing to go to extreme lengths to protect them and her city.
